        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<section class=\"lc-page-intro\">\n  <div class=\"lc-page-intro__inner\">\n    <header class=\"lc-page-intro__header\">\n      <h1 class=\"lc-page-intro__title\">Curtains, Blinds and Hardware</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"lc-page-intro__text rte\" id=\"lc-page-intro-text\">\n      <p>\n        Curtains, blinds, and hardware are essential elements in creating comfortable, stylish, and functional hospitality spaces. Our range offers tailored solutions for hotels, guesthouses, lodges, and luxury suites, designed to provide effective light control, privacy, and a polished finish that enhances every room.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        Choose from blockout and self-lined curtains suited to guest rooms and public areas. Our blinds collection includes wood, eco wood, aluminium, zebra, and Venetian styles, offering versatile options to meet diverse design and operational needs.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        Complete your window treatments with commercial-grade curtain hardware available in black steel, antique brass, stainless steel, and bronze finishes. These durable rods, brackets, finials, and accessories support professional installation and long-lasting performance in high-use environments.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        Whether you are outfitting new developments, refurbishing existing properties, or upgrading premium suites, custom <strong>sizing</strong> and expert guidance help you select the right solution for your space.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.linenco.co.za/pages/trade-registration-form\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Apply for trade pricing</strong></a> or contact us on <a href=\"tel:0101094950\"><strong>010 109 4950</strong></a> or WhatsApp <a href=\"https://wa.me/27662918292\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>066 291 8292</strong></a>.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"lc-read-more\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"lc-page-intro-text\">\n      Read more\n    </button>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .lc-page-intro {\n    padding: 32px 0;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__inner {\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 0 24px;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__header {\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__title {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-size: 28px;\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin-bottom: 0;\n    transition: max-height 0.35s ease;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__text p {\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__text p:last-child {\n    margin-bottom: 0;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__text a {\n    text-decoration: none;\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .lc-page-intro__text a:hover,\n  .lc-page-intro__text a:focus {\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    text-underline-offset: 3px;\n  }\n  /* Collapsed state - showing 4 lines */\n  .lc-page-intro__text.is-collapsed {\n    max-height: 8.4em; /* 4 lines × 1.5 line-height × 14px font-size = 84px */\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .lc-read-more {\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 0;\n    margin-top: 10px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    text-decoration: underline;\n    text-underline-offset: 3px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n    transition: opacity 0.2s;\n  }\n  .lc-read-more:hover,\n  .lc-read-more:focus {\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .lc-page-intro {\n      padding: 22px 0;\n    }\n    .lc-page-intro__inner {\n      padding: 0 12px;\n    }\n    .lc-page-intro__title {\n      font-size: 22px;\n      line-height: 1.2;\n    }\n    .lc-page-intro__text {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    .lc-read-more {\n      font-size: 12px;\n    }\n    .lc-page-intro__text.is-collapsed {\n      max-height: 7.7em; /* 4 lines at mobile: 4 × 1.6 × 12px ≈ 77px */\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\n    var section = document.querySelector('.lc-page-intro');\n    if (!section) return;\n\n    var text = section.querySelector('#lc-page-intro-text');\n    var btn = section.querySelector('.lc-read-more');\n    if (!text || !btn) return;\n\n    // Start collapsed\n    text.classList.add('is-collapsed');\n\n    // Hide button if content doesn't overflow\n    if (text.scrollHeight <= text.clientHeight + 2) {\n      btn.style.display = 'none';\n      return;\n    }\n\n    btn.addEventListener('click', function () {\n      var expanded = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';\n\n      if (!expanded) {\n        text.classList.remove('is-collapsed');\n        btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n        btn.textContent = 'Read less';\n      } else {\n        text.classList.add('is-collapsed');\n        btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n        btn.textContent = 'Read more';\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
        "text_alignment": "start"
      }
